well i would have to assume first if you're going to 
do something like this that you've probably got a

01:50.495 --> 02:16.350
limited number of freshmen that you would want to 
enroll and of course what you want to do is get those

01:50.495 --> 02:16.350
who you think would be the most successful or most 
likely to complete the curriculum in probably

02:17.360 --> 02:26.933
prescribed, quote, four-year time?

