key as to why they did or did not perform as well as

03:33.128 --> 03:41.919
they did. I think it boils down to if you really want 
to

03:43.401 --> 04:02.865
select those students who may be best able to 
profit by the education, that you're going to have

03:43.401 --> 04:02.865
to do a review, an individual review. I don't think 
you can do it just on giving weighted points to

04:05.647 --> 04:15.321
various and certain aspects of the thing. If you 
can throw in an interview I think it's even better.

04:19.647 --> 04:26.557
