think it's probably better without the parents,

04:55.246 --> 04:57.949
for the most part. Sometimes an interview with the 
parents without the student gives you some

04:59.611 --> 05:03.876
insight, too. Again, we're talking about how much 
time you're able to spend in the selection

05:04.597 --> 05:09.903
process. And the more time you can spend up to a 
certain point, probably the better job you can do.

05:15.850 --> 05:20.355
