09:23.656 --> 09:43.442
the thing, where if they've got to spend the money 
educating more undergraduates, then there's

09:23.656 --> 09:43.442
less at other levels. It's a matter of economics, I 
think. Obviously, being an Aggie, I would think

09:46.126 --> 09:51.773
everybody ought to be an Aggie, but the university

09:53.980 --> 10:03.512
From a personal standpoint, I think it has gotten 
so large that it's hard to have the personal

